/*
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
STATIC BLOCK
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Static block runs when class is loaded.

It runs ONLY ONCE regardless of how many objects are created.

Example:

static {
    grade = 8;
}

Execution order:

1 Class loads
2 Static block executes
3 Objects are created

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Use cases:

• Initialize static variables
• Load configuration
• Database driver loading

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

INTERVIEW POINT

Static block runs before main().

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/